## Why This Is Asked

Tests for serverless, multi-tenant extension sandboxes require robust isolation guarantees, quota enforcement under burst loads, and reliable event delivery semantics. This question evaluates your ability to architect end-to-end test flows that encompass test data seeding, observability instrumentation, concurrency handling, and comprehensive failure mode validation across tenant boundaries.

## Key Concepts

